reviewText: which is what I wanted! It's actually a music video shot in three cities - Hong Kong, Bali and New York City - mostly at night. Shows fashion shows, clubbing (with the emphasis on young females), street scenes and city skylines(beautiful). Not what I was looking for or am interested in. Found the music obnoxious but that's probably because I'm a "woman of a certain age"! Young people would probably find it all very exciting.
